IngestEventRequest.description:
Accepts BOTH formats:

New (current):
  {
    "event": "test.event",
    "timestamp": "...",
    "properties": {...}
  }

Legacy (common):
  {
    "type": "test.event",
    "timestamp": "...",
    "payload": {...}
  }

Also accepts (user attempted):
  {
    "event": { "type": "...", "payload": {...} },
    "timestamp": "..."
  }
